metadata.name: FIRST POETS TOMB
metadata.description:
It is fabled that after the first poet died, his followers gathered and created a majestic mausoleum for him, which is still guarded by a guardian ghost to this day. 
This series intends to explore the lost worlds in combination with creator's imagination.
